&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years&lt;/strong&gt; in community engagement, advocacy, public affairs, or nonprofit partnership roles—or equivalent consulting experience in public-facing programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success &lt;strong&gt;building trust&lt;/strong&gt; with community organizations, especially &lt;strong&gt;disability, senior, and equity-focused&lt;/strong&gt; stakeholders; comfortable in politically sensitive environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience &lt;strong&gt;facilitating&lt;/strong&gt; trainings, focus groups, and partner meetings; strong facilitator, not only a planner.&lt;/li&gt;
