&lt;li&gt;Scale community-specific programs by identifying winning local tactics and developing the replicable processes and playbooks needed to deploy them in similar markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage data reporting and dashboards, tracking key metrics to communicate clear strategies and actionable insights to both internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 6+ years of experience with a strong interest in growth marketing and a demonstrated ability to turn data into actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer-centric storyteller with exceptional written and interpersonal communication skills, particularly in explaining complex ideas to diverse audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resourceful, a problem solver who is motivated by high levels of ownership and the opportunity to have a measurable impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, a critical thinker with a no-task-too-small attitude while navigating a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical and data-oriented, excited to develop your quantitative skills and turn data into insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
