&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Final salary will be determined by the candidate’s experience, knowledge, and skills. Salary reflected does not include equity or variable pay, where applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Range: $125,000-$160,000&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are proud to offer a generous and comprehensive benefits package, including free medical plans, 401K matching, catered lunch on Wednesdays, and many other perks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
