&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Diesel &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mechanic&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;at SAM by Via, you will perform preventative maintenance and minor repairs on buses, automotive equipment, and shop equipment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
