&lt;li&gt;Influence technology and process adoption to improve regional efficiency and visibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to company-wide ops priorities&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
