&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Final salary will be determined by the candidate’s experience, knowledge, and skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary reflected does not include equity or variable pay, where applicable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Range: $150,000-$210,000&lt;/li&gt;
